        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 1 at 10:30AM CDT until August 1 at 6:00PM CDT by NWS Shreveport LA</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Heat index values up to 106 to 109 are possible.

* WHERE...Portions of north central and northwest Louisiana and deep
east Texas.

* WHEN...From 2 PM this afternoon to 6 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
